Legendary musician, Innocent Idibia, widely known as 2baba has been confirmed as the guest artiste to entertain at the fifth anniversary of popular nightclub Silver Fox on Saturday February 15. Silver Fix which is arguably the biggest nightlife entertainment club in Africa has been running for half a decade. Themed “Legend Celebrates Legend” the event will have a guest appearance and performance from music legend, 2Baba, who has proved his legacy for over two decades. It will be a reminder of dominance, consistency and luxury lifestyle the renowned nightlife brand is respected for. Other side attractions include a special Cleopatra costume dance and several giveaways.